      </div>
      <p>Dear&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        <span class='name1'>{{name}}</span>
        ,<br />
      </p>
      <p>Congratulations.<br />
        Your account's status has been changed to
        <span class='active'>Active</span>
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>You are again free to login on our e-commerce</p>
      <p>Regards,</p>
    </div>
